org.zanata.rest.service

Interface CopyTransResource


  • @Path(value="/copytrans")
 @Produces(value={"application/xml","application/json"})
 @Consumes(value={"application/xml","application/json"})
public interface CopyTransResource
    Represents the state of a copy trans run. These are special processes which search for and reuse translations.
    Author:
    Carlos Munoz camunoz@redhat.com
